  "Description": {
    "English": "As the boundaries of reality begin to weaken, the risk of <span class=\"name name-special\">catastrophic breach anomalies</span> increases.<br><br>This ancient artifact radiates with a spectral energy, increasing the <span class=\"name name-special\">boundary strength</span> within the local area and guarding against reality continuity errors.<br><br>Must be constructed within the boundaries of a <span class=\"name name-stellar\">habitable base</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "随着现实的边界不断崩塌，发生<span class=\"name name-special\">灾难性裂隙异象</span>的风险正在不断上升。<br><br>这种古代遗物散发着的特殊灵体能量能够提高有效范围内的<span class=\"name name-special\">边界强度</span>并抵御现实连续性的崩坏。<br><br>必须在<span class=\"name name-stellar\">宜居基地</span>的边界内进行建造。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "隨著現實邊界開始變得脆弱，<span class=\"name name-special\">災難性異常裂痕</span>出現機率提升。<br><br>這件古老器物散發著光譜能量，加固了局部範圍內的<span class=\"name name-special\">邊界強度</span>，以防現實連續性發生錯誤。<br><br>必須在<span class=\"name name-stellar\">可居住基地</span>範圍內建造。"
  },
